                                    <li class="change-item">
                                        <span class="badge type-imp">Improved</span>
                                        <span><strong>Audit Logs:</strong> More detailed deployment and access logs for compliance.</span>
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="change-item">
                                        <span class="badge type-fix">Fix</span>
                                        <span><strong>Permissions:</strong> Fixed a bug with team invites and access roles.</span>
